subtitleNullable: This is a faster parquet version of train.csv from the janestreet
descriptionNullable:
### Brief Introduction

This is a faster `.parquet` format version converted from the [jane street market prediction data](https://www.kaggle.com/c/jane-street-market-prediction/data)
You can use `pandas.read_parquet()` function to read this data like this:
```
data = pd.read_parquet('../input/janestreet-parquet/train.parquet')
```
